  "title": "Chief Executive Officer (CEO)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job descriptions</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develop and implement the company’s vision, mission, and overall strategy.</li>\n  <li>Identify and pursue growth opportunities, including new markets and product lines.</li>\n  <li>Oversee daily operations, ensuring efficiency and effectiveness across all departments.</li>\n  <li>Monitor key performance indicators (KPIs) to measure company performance and make data-driven decisions.</li>\n  <li>Ensure financial health through effective budgeting, forecasting, and financial reporting.</li>\n  <li>Manage relationships with investors, stakeholders, and financial institutions.</li>\n  <li>Foster a positive company culture and empower leadership teams.</li>\n  <li>Oversee talent acquisition, development, and retention strategies.</li>\n  <li>Build and maintain strong relationships with clients, suppliers, and industry partners.</li>\n  <li>Represent the company at industry events, conferences, and public engagements.</li>\n  <li>Promote a culture of innovation and continuous improvement within the organization.</li>\n  <li>Stay updated on industry trends and emerging technologies to maintain competitive advantage.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>A degree in Mechanical Engineering, Electro Engineering, Mechatronic Technology or a related field.</li>\n  <li>5-10 years leadership experiences in manufacturing sector or senior executive role, gained from working your way up the corporate ladder through various roles and jobs.</li>\n  <li>Deep understanding of machinery and parts manufacturing processes, technologies, and market dynamics.</li>\n  <li>Excellence leadership, change management, and communication skills.</li>\n  <li>Strong analytical, decision-making, and problem-solving skills.</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with industry regulations, safety standards, and quality control processes.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Skills required</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Communication skills</li>\n  <li>Negotiation skill</li>\n  <li>Leadership skill</li>\n  <li>Strategic Thinking skills</li>\n  <li>Problem-solving skills</li>\n</ul>",
